{"tid":1940683,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印尼缺防護物資 7醫護殉職","createTime":"2020-03-24T02:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:00:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eae4524fff598aeea71f075ee1a07ace5635a27a","tid":1940683,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/UUOE7NTUWRDPE7QTQS4VSMJU4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FUUOE7NTUWRDPE7QTQS4VSMJU4E%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1uu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=dc2f83ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FUUOE7NTUWRDPE7QTQS4VSMJU4E%2F&h=77a8ad7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/UUOE7NTUWRDPE7QTQS4VSMJU4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n印尼缺防護物資 7醫護殉職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200324/large/1584976673_14d6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200324%2Flarge%2F1584976673_14d6.gif&h=5dd5524b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼工作人員在巴士噴消毒劑。<br />\n<br />\n印尼武漢肺炎確診個案近600宗，前日有七名醫生和護士證實染病逝世。有醫護人員反映，當地防護物資短缺，而且疫情資訊欠透明，令他們難以防備。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：酒吧轟不公：食飯唔會播毒？<br />\n<br />\n穿便利雨衣運患者轉院<br />\n<br />\n印尼政府是前日才首次證實有參與抗疫的醫護殉職，醫學會理事會其後透露死者涉及六名醫生，並為他們哀悼。當地媒體則報道，另有一名37歲、負責照顧武漢肺炎患者的護士過世。印尼大學公共衞生系流行病學專家潘杜是其中一名殉職醫生的親戚，他批評政府無法為醫護人員提供足夠的個人防護裝備，令人難以原諒。<br />\n<br />\n印尼多處早已傳出防護物資短缺，其中西爪哇省南部打橫市有醫護人員日前疑缺乏防護衣，要穿着藍色便利雨衣運送武漢肺炎患者轉院。打橫市衞生官員承認便利雨衣防護力不足，但整個打橫市只有10套個人防護裝備分配給各醫院，因此買了100套雨衣給醫護人員。另外，東爪哇泗水的艾爾朗加大學總醫院也坦言因肺炎患者湧入，防護衣和口罩都快用完，如果無法補給，就只能使用雨衣。<br />\n<br />\n該國疫情資訊欠透明亦為人詬病。一名去世護士的同袍透露，在過去禽流感爆發時，她們都知道病人狀況，對工作有很大幫助，但這次武漢肺炎卻無法得知疑似患者是否確診，坦言感擔心。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"92aab110d34ace517776dd1581c9ca7c712ab21d","tid":1940683,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"香港幾萬盒sensi 現貨任買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1e1edf8425f1bd8c1aba2a25117bc01466dc8d","tid":1940683,"uid":8762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92aab110d34ace517776dd1581c9ca7c712ab21d","tid":1940683,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"香港幾萬盒sensi 現貨任買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦攞sensi 入病房應該死多幾件"},{"pid":"034c532327f3d4134e8384b1ee656552dc6951c5","tid":1940683,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"記住要排華，送班支那人返支那。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0f6ce710b61c2e737c859cd7887918b61af75d","tid":1940683,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af1e1edf8425f1bd8c1aba2a25117bc01466dc8d","tid":1940683,"uid":8762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92aab110d34ace517776dd1581c9ca7c712ab21d","tid":1940683,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"香港幾萬盒sensi 現貨任買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦攞sensi 入病房應該死多幾件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"印尼醫護好似真係用sensi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br /